 Third Man宣布首位澳大利亚签约The Belair Lip Bombs https://www.nme.com/news/music/third-man-announce-first-australian-signing-the-belair-lip-bombs-3781026?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=third-man-announce-first-澳大利亚签署贝莱尔唇形炸弹Emma WilkesMon, 05 Aug 2024 13:58:04 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3781026 <p><img width="2048" height="1365" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Belair_Lip_Bombs_EXTRA_WEB_by_Ian_Laidlaw-225.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Belair 唇部炸弹" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Belair_Lip_Bombs_EXTRA_WEB_by_Ian_Laidlaw-225.jpg 2048w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Belair_Lip_Bombs_EXTRA_WEB_by_Ian_Laidlaw-225-400x267.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Belair_Lip_Bombs_EXTRA_WEB_by_Ian_Laidlaw-225-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Belair_Lip_Bombs_EXTRA_WEB_by_Ian_Laidlaw-225-696x464.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Belair_Lip_Bombs_EXTRA_WEB_by_Ian_Laidlaw-225-1392x928.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Belair_Lip_Bombs_EXTRA_WEB_by_Ian_Laidlaw-225-1068x712.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px" /></p><p>该厂牌将于十月以实体形式重新发行首张专辑《Lush Life》</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/third-man-announce-first-australian-signing-the-belair-lip-bombs-3781026">《Third Man》宣布首位澳大利亚签约 The Belair Lip Bombs 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2048" height="1365" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Belair_Lip_Bombs_EXTRA_WEB_by_Ian_Laidlaw-225.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Belair 唇部炸弹" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Belair_Lip_Bombs_EXTRA_WEB_by_Ian_Laidlaw-225.jpg 2048w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Belair_Lip_Bombs_EXTRA_WEB_by_Ian_Laidlaw-225-400x267.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Belair_Lip_Bombs_EXTRA_WEB_by_Ian_Laidlaw-225-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Belair_Lip_Bombs_EXTRA_WEB_by_Ian_Laidlaw-225-696x464.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Belair_Lip_Bombs_EXTRA_WEB_by_Ian_Laidlaw-225-1392x928.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Belair_Lip_Bombs_EXTRA_WEB_by_Ian_Laidlaw-225-1068x712.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-belair-lip-bombs">Belair Lip Bombs</a>成为第一支与 Third Man Records 签约的澳大利亚乐队。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/belair-lip-bombs-lush-life-review-3485795">Belair Lip Bombs 的“Lush Life”融合了能量和实验</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队去年通过 Cousin Will 发行了他们的首张专辑《Lush Life》，现在将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-white">Jack White</a>的厂牌重新发行。实体版将于 10 月 18 日起发售。</p><p> “与 Third Man 签约对我们来说是一个梦想，特别是作为该厂牌上的第一支澳大利亚乐队，”乐队表示。 “该厂牌的每个人都是传奇人物，很明显他们对每张专辑都投入了多少热爱。能够加入第三人大家庭，我们感到无比兴奋！”</p><p> Belair Lip Bombs 正在制作他们的第二张专辑，预计将于明年发行。 </p><figure id="attachment_3781046" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3781046" style="width: 900px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3781046" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/LushLife_AlbumCover-9900000000079e3c.jpeg" alt="Belair 唇部炸弹" width="900" height="900" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/LushLife_AlbumCover-9900000000079e3c.jpeg 900w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/LushLife_AlbumCover-9900000000079e3c-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/LushLife_AlbumCover-9900000000079e3c-400x400.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/LushLife_AlbumCover-9900000000079e3c-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/LushLife_AlbumCover-9900000000079e3c-696x696.jpeg 696w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3781046" class="wp-caption-text"> Belair Lip Bombs 的 Lush Life 艺术作品。图片来源：奥利弗·布鲁克斯</figcaption></figure><p>在谈到《Lush Life》首次发布时，主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maisie-everett">Maisie Everett</a>说道：“这张专辑的标题是《Lush Life》——这句话在整张专辑中被多次引用。专辑中探索的主题或主题通常涉及对不存在的东西的渴望，但可能不太清楚那东西是什么。 “Lush Life”一词描述了一个完美的世界，一切都很容易（但实际上并不存在）。</p><p> “我希望它是完美的，我们在录音室里尝试了很多不同的东西，包括旋律和和声。这很有趣。当时我在另一个乐队中演奏，并且不断地巡回演出，这使得我很难以线性方式完成这张专辑。但我很高兴我们花时间去做，因为结果正是我们想要的。”</p><p> <em>NME</em>在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/belair-lip-bombs-lush-life-review-3485795">《Lush Life》</a>的四星评论中写道：“在 The Belair Lip Bombs 中，Everett 处于前沿和中心位置，不仅背离了[前乐队] <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/clamm">CLAMM</a>怒气冲冲的后朋克风格，而且在一系列充满活力的风格。</p><p> “事实上，首张专辑《Lush Life》有一种不拘一格的品质，这在其他乐队中可能听起来不够集中，但埃弗雷特和他的公司在每首歌曲上都经过了磨练和控制，我们在每一个转弯和侧步中都能保持正确的状态。这些歌曲简短而朗朗上口，贝斯手吉米·德劳顿和鼓手利亚姆·德布鲁因为迈克·布拉维卡多才多艺的主音吉他和埃弗雷特同样多变的声乐转变提供了坚定不移的动力。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/third-man-announce-first-australian-signing-the-belair-lip-bombs-3781026">《Third Man》宣布首位澳大利亚签约 The Belair Lip Bombs 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
